{"about_the_game":"<strong>You play as a very lazy capybara who has to climb a mountain to take a bath in his barrel!</strong><br><br>It seemed that the capybara had already accepted her fate of not being able to take a bath. Prepare for the falls, try not to fall and keep going. Travel through different eras and reach the top of the mountain!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732980/extras/v3__4_.gif?t=1725017725\" /> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732980/extras/v4__3_.gif?t=1725017725\" /><br><br>You have a rope with a barrel to balance while climbing.<br>Use all your experience to hold on to the capybara.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732980/extras/CGif4.gif?t=1725017725\" /><br><br>There are several locations in the game: <br>  \ud83d\udc2a Walk through ancient architecture!<br>  \u2694\ufe0f See medieval houses and walk through narrow streets!<br>  \ud83c\udf35 Wild West - Walk through a small base and out into the mines!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732980/extras/CGif5.gif?t=1725017725\" /><br><br>  \ud83c\udf5cThe City - Stroll down an anime inspired street! <br>  \u26f0\ufe0f Climb a mountain and take a bath!<br>  \u262f If you suddenly fall off the mountain, there's a small chance you'll end up on the roof of a steampunk building!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732980/extras/CGif3.gif?t=1725017725\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Take the first step","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2732980/08aab802f9c11ffa0d6b688f856dda0e33341e9e.jpg"},{"name":"Road to Egypt!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2732980/927cd1744a